2009年4月1日，[[倫敦市|倫敦市]]报贩'''伊恩·汤姆林森'''在[[2009年二十国集团伦敦峰会抗议示威|2009年二十国集团伦敦峰会抗议示威]]期间被警察推倒在地后死亡。经过[[死因研讯|死因研讯]]，陪审团裁定受害人死于警察[[不合法被殺|行凶杀人]]，涉案警员西蒙·哈伍德受[[誤殺|过失杀人罪]]起诉。法庭裁定罪名不成立，但哈伍德仍因行为严重不当被开除警队<ref name="WalkerLewis19July2012">{{cite news | author1 = Peter Walker | author2 = Paul Lewis | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2012-07-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201103153915/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/19/simon-harwood-not-guilty-ian-tomlinson | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/19/simon-harwood-not-guilty-ian-tomlinson | title = Ian Tomlinson death: Simon Harwood cleared of manslaughter | archivedate = 2020-11-03 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Peter Walker | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2012-09-17 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/17/simon-harwood-sacked-gross-misconduct | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200420034808/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/17/simon-harwood-sacked-gross-misconduct | title = Ian Tomlinson case: PC Simon Harwood sacked for gross misconduct | archivedate = 2020-04-20 | accessdate = 2020-11-05 }}</ref>。经过民事涉讼，[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]向汤姆林森的家人支付未公开数额的赔偿，承认哈伍德的行为导致汤姆林森死亡<ref name="auto1">{{cite news | author = Matthew Taylor | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101014222/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2013/aug/05/ian-tomlinson-apology-met-police | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2013/aug/05/ian-tomlinson-apology-met-police | title = Ian Tomlinson's family win apology from Met police over death in 2009 | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2013-08-05 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-05 | archivedate = 2020-11-01 }}</ref>。

首次[[驗屍|驗屍]]认定受害人死于心脏病发，《卫报》一周后公布倫敦警察廳警员用警棍击打汤姆林森腿部、随后又将他推倒在地的视频。受害人没有参与抗议，当时准备经过警戒线回家。倒地后他一度起身离开，但很快再度倒地并在几分钟后死亡。<ref name="LewisvideoApril7">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021013456/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/07/ian-tomlinson-g20-death-video | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/07/ian-tomlinson-g20-death-video | title = Ian Tomlinson death: Guardian video reveals police attack on man who died at G20 protest | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-07 | accessdate = 2020-11-05 | archivedate = 2020-10-21 }}</ref>

[[英国独立监察警方处理投诉委员会|英国独立监察警方处理投诉委员会]]开展刑事调查，再次验尸结果表明汤姆林森死于腹部钝器伤结合[[肝硬化|肝硬化]]引发的内出血。考虑到几次验尸结论不同，无法证明死亡与殴打之间的因果关系，[[英格蘭及威爾斯皇家檢控署|皇家檢控署]]决定不起诉哈伍德。<ref name="CPSstatement">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101100317/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/cps-statement-death-ian-tomlinson | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/cps-statement-death-ian-tomlinson | title = CPS statement on the death of Ian Tomlinson | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2010-07-22 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-11-01 }}</ref>但2011年陪审团裁定受害人死于警察行凶杀人后，皇家检控署改变立场以过失杀人罪起诉<ref name="Starmerreview">{{cite news | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-05-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307213022/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/video/2011/may/24/ian-tomlinson-police-manslaughter-video | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | title = Statement from Keir Starmer | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/video/2011/may/24/ian-tomlinson-police-manslaughter-video }}</ref>。2012年法庭裁定哈伍德罪名不成立，但他几个月后就被开除<ref name="WalkerLewis19July2012" />。

汤姆林森之死在英国引发警察、媒体、公众和独立监察警方处理投诉委员会独立地位关系的大讨论<ref name="Lyall">{{cite news | author = Sarah Lyall | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2009-05-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031073704/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/31/world/europe/31police.html?pagewanted=all | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/31/world/europe/31police.html?pagewanted=all | title = Critics Assail British Police for Harsh Tactics During the G-20 Summit Meeting | archivedate = 2020-10-31 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-05 }}</ref>。面对外界疑虑，[[女皇陛下警务、消防和救援服务监督局|警务总监督]][[丹尼斯·奥康纳|丹尼斯·奥康纳]]于2009年11月公布150页的报告，希望恢复市民对警方的信任<ref name="LewisLavilleNov25">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = Sandra Laville | accessdate = 2020-11-05 | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030230856/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2009/nov/25/police-g20-inquiry-report | url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2009/nov/25/police-g20-inquiry-report | title = G20 report lays down the law to police on use of force | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-11-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
=== 伊恩·汤姆林森 ===
伊恩·汤姆林森（{{lang|en|Ian Tomlinson}}）生于[[德比郡|德比郡]][[馬特洛克|馬特洛克]]，父亲叫吉姆·汤姆林森（{{lang|en|Jim Tomlinson}}），母亲叫安·汤姆林森（{{lang|en|Ann Tomlinson}}）。他在17岁时移居伦敦，靠搭建[[脚手架|脚手架]]安身立命。事发时，汤姆林森是伦敦《晚间标准报》（{{lang|en|''Evening Standard''}}）的临时销售员。<ref>{{cite news | author = Robert Booth | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/08/ian-tomlinson-friends-tributes | title = Friends of G20 protests victim shocked by loss of 'lovable man' | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-08 | accessdate = 2020-11-05 | archivedate = 2016-09-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160927191926/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/08/ian-tomlinson-friends-tributes }}</ref>汤姆林森结过两次婚，儿子和孙辈共有九人，他长期酗酒，因此已与第二任妻子朱莉亚（{{lang|en|Julia}}）分居13年，曾长时间居无定所。2008年，他开始住进伦敦[[史密斯菲爾德_(倫敦)|史密斯菲爾德]]林赛街（{{lang|en|Lindsey Street}}）收容无家可归人士的林赛旅店<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101050550/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/london/7990649.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/london/7990649.stm | title = G20 death video 'touches' family | work = BBC News | date = 2008-04-08 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archivedate = 2020-11-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Jon Swaine | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2009-04-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161010074717/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/5137178/G20-death-Police-gave-Ian-Tomlinson-a-good-beating-says-his-father.html | archivedate = 2016-10-10 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/5137178/G20-death-Police-gave-Ian-Tomlinson-a-good-beating-says-his-father.html | title = G20 death: Police gave Ian Tomlinson a 'good beating', says his father | accessdate = 2020-11-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2011-03-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030164806/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8413482/Ian-Tomlinson-profile-homeless-alcoholic-who-was-not-even-part-of-G20-protests.html | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8413482/Ian-Tomlinson-profile-homeless-alcoholic-who-was-not-even-part-of-G20-protests.html | title = Ian Tomlinson profile: homeless alcoholic who was not even part of G20 protests | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-05 }}</ref>。事发时他正经过伦敦金融区前往林赛旅店，路上多处被警戒线阻挡。此前他在[[銀行及紀念碑站|銀行及紀念碑站]]外、[[伦敦大火纪念碑|伦敦大火纪念碑]]旁的报摊和朋友巴里·史密斯（{{lang|en|Barry Smith}}）一起工作，准备沿老路线回家。<ref name="BrownApril9">{{cite news | author = David Brown | accessdate = 2020-11-05 | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/ian-tomlinson-see-you-tomorrow-barry-if-im-still-living-and-breathing-xplbr0t7xbd | title = Ian Tomlinson: 'See you tomorrow, Barry, if I'm still living and breathing' | newspaper = The Times | date = 2009-04-09 | archivedate = 2009-05-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090516235851/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/uk/article6062637.ece }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Millwall fan dies during G20 riots | newspaper = South London Press | date = 2009-04-06}}</ref>

=== 伦敦警察厅，英国独立监察警方处理投诉委员会 ===
[[File:G20_mounted_police.jpg|thumb]]期间的伦敦骑警]]

[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]拥有4.4万多警力，是英国最大的警队<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2020-11-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811224245/https://www.met.police.uk/police-forces/metropolitan-police/areas/about-us/about-the-met/structure/ | title = Structure | publisher = Metropolitan Police | archivedate = 2020-08-11 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.met.police.uk/police-forces/metropolitan-police/areas/about-us/about-the-met/structure/ }}</ref>。整个[[大倫敦|大倫敦]]除金融区[[倫敦市|倫敦市]]由[[倫敦市警察|倫敦市警察]]负责外，其他区域的警务均属伦敦警察厅职责。事件发生时的[[伦敦警察厅总监|伦敦警察厅总监]]是[[保罗·斯蒂芬森|保罗·斯蒂芬森]]（{{lang|en|Paul Stephenson}}）爵士，伦敦市警察总监是迈克·鲍伦（{{lang|en|Mike Bowron}}）。伦敦警察厅受[[首都警察監管局|首都警察監管局]]监管，当时的主管是[[倫敦市長_(大倫敦)|伦敦市长]][[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]。<ref>{{cite news | author = Richard Edwards | date = 2009-03-20 | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200509054121/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5023042/G20-to-be-most-expensive-police-operation-in-British-history.html | archivedate = 2020-05-09 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5023042/G20-to-be-most-expensive-police-operation-in-British-history.html | title = G20 to be most expensive police operation in British history | deadurl = no }}</ref>

欧打并推倒受害人的是伦敦警察厅[[地区支援课|地区支援课]]警员，可通过肩章编号上的字母“{{lang|en|U}}”辨别。地区支援课警员穿戴军用风格头盔、阻燃制服、防刺背心和[[巴拉克拉瓦头套|巴拉克拉瓦头套]]，专门维持公共秩序。事发时的行动指挥是总警司米克·约翰逊（{{lang|en|Mick Johnson}}）。<ref>{{cite news | author = Jon Swaine | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180105040740/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5127064/G20-death-what-is-the-Metropolitan-Polices-Territorial-Support-Group.html | archivedate = 2018-01-05 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5127064/G20-death-what-is-the-Metropolitan-Polices-Territorial-Support-Group.html | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | title = G20 death: what is the Metropolitan Police's Territorial Support Group? | date = 2009-04-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Sandra Laville | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101140757/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/16/g20-tomlinson-ipcc-investigation-protest-police | title = Specialist protest squads at centre of investigations into G20 police violence | deadurl = no | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/16/g20-tomlinson-ipcc-investigation-protest-police | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2010-04-16 | archivedate = 2020-11-01 }}</ref>{{refn|group="注"|地区支援课的前身是[[特别巡逻课|特别巡逻课]]（{{lang|en|Special Patrol Group}}），因1979年涉嫌在伦敦打死示威人士[[布莱尔·皮奇之死|布莱尔·皮奇]]（{{lang|en|Blair Peach}}）臭名远扬<ref>{{cite news | author = Harry Underwood | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141205020123/http://www.theweek.co.uk/arts-life/24061/blair-peach-30-years-death-protestor | url = http://www.theweek.co.uk/arts-life/24061/blair-peach-30-years-death-protestor | title = Blair Peach, 30 years on: death of a protestor | newspaper = The First Post | date = 2009-04-08 | accessdate = 2014-12-05 | archivedate = 2014-12-05 }}</ref>。}}

英国独立监察警方处理投诉委员会由《2002年警察改革法》组建，2004年开始运作，用于取代与警方关系密切引起公众不满的警察投诉管理局，事发时[[尼克·哈德威克|尼克·哈德威克]]（{{lang|en|Nick Hardwick}}）任主席。与警察投诉管理局相比，独立监察警方处理投诉委员会运作与负责英格兰和威尔士刑事司法及警务的[[英國內政部|英國內政部]]独立。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8466268.stm | title = How well does the IPCC police the police? | work = [[BBC新闻|BBC News]] | date = 2010-01-18 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2020-11-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201103224436/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8466268.stm | deadurl = no }}</ref>

=== 格伦科行动 ===
[[File:G20_crowd_and_police_lines.jpg|thumb]]门外]]

[[2009年二十国集团伦敦峰会|2009年二十国集团伦敦峰会]]的安保代号“格伦科行动”（{{lang|en|Operation Glencoe}}），由伦敦警察厅、伦敦市警局和[[英国交通警察|英国交通警察]]（{{lang|en|British Transport Police}}）合作，共同听命于伦敦警察厅[[金银铜应急指挥体系|金级指挥]][[鲍勃·布罗德赫斯特|鲍勃·布罗德赫斯特]]（{{lang|en|Bob Broadhurst}}）<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2009-07-30 | url = http://cms.met.police.uk/news/updates/operation_glencoe_policing_and_security_for_the_g20_london_summit | title = Operation Glencoe policing and security for the G20 London Summit | deadurl = yes | date = 2009-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090730204636/http://cms.met.police.uk/news/updates/operation_glencoe_policing_and_security_for_the_g20_london_summit | archivedate = 2009-07-30 | publisher = Metropolitan Police Service }}</ref>{{refn|group="注"|据《卫报》报导，抗议示威人士猜测行动代号是以1692年[[格伦科惨案|格伦科惨案]]命名<ref name="GuardianGlencoe"/>。伦敦警察厅发言人曾对抗议示威群众称，警方“已经做好准备”，群众认为他的意思是警方准备再现格伦科惨案，伦敦警察厅表示这纯属断章取义<ref>{{cite book | title = Demonstrating Respect for Rights | work = Joint Committee on Human Rights | publisher = House of Commons | date = 2009-07-28 | page = 13}}</ref>。示威者火上浇油，宣称要占据中伦敦并将银行家私刑处死<ref name="GuardianGlencoe">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = Sandra Laville | author3 = John Vidal | url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/mar/28/g20-protests-london | title = G20 protests: Cry havoc – and let slip a rainbow alliance of summit protesters | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-03-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200509113641/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/mar/28/g20-protests-london | archivedate = 2020-05-09 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 }}</ref>。}}。

2009年4月1日共发生六起抗议示威，分别是[[倫敦展覽中心|倫敦展覽中心]]的安全行动、[[英国停战联盟|停战]]游行、[[中国驻英国大使馆|中国大使馆]]外的[[西藏独立运动|西藏独立运动]]抗议示威、[[人与地球|人与地球]]（{{lang|en|People & Planet}}）抗议示威、气候行动营抗议示威、以及[[英格兰银行|英格兰银行]]外的抗议示威。气候营和英格兰银行的示威人数超过四千。4月1日出动的警察超过5500，次日2800，成本720万英镑。警察需连续执勤14小时，中间连吃饭的时间都没有，到午夜才能躺在警局地板上睡觉，早上七点又要上岗。崩紧的神经和气氛令局势更加紧张，加大警察工作难度。<ref name="OConnor2009p22">{{cite web | author = Denis O'Connor | title = Adapting to protest | url = http://www.met.police.uk/news/docs/g20_final_report.pdf | archivedate = 2009-08-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webarchive.org.uk/wayback/archive/20090824024746/http://www.met.police.uk/news/docs/g20_final_report.pdf | work = Her Majesty's Chief Inspector of Constabulary | year = 2009 | pages = cover page, 22, 23, 33 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7955057.stm | title = Police warn of G20 protest scale | work = BBC News | date = 2009-03-20 | archivedate = 2019-09-30 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190930205619/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7955057.stm | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Lyall" />

中午12点半到下午19点，警方采用“遏制”战术将英格兰银行的人群控制在原地，媒体称为“[[沸水戰術|包抄战术]]”，把示威者包围在狭小空间，直到警察把他们驱散<ref name="LewisLavilleJuly7">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = Sandra Laville | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030012839/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2009/jul/07/g20-protests-police-tactics | url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2009/jul/07/g20-protests-police-tactics | title = G20 police authorised to use reasonable force minutes before Tomlinson died | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-07-07 }}</ref><ref name="OConnor2009p22" />。下午七点，高级警官认为有必要使用“合理武力”驱散银行周围示威者<ref name="LewisLavilleJuly7" />。七点十分到四十分，人群涌向警察，有人投掷[[拋體|物品]]，警方用盾牌阻挡。混战爆发，警察开始逮捕人员，就在此时，汤姆林森从旁边经过准备回家<ref name="OConnor2009p22" />{{rp|79}}<ref name="Lyall" />。

== 事发 ==
=== 初遇警察 ===
