许多报纸刊发事发当天汤姆林森初遇警察的图像。据巴里·史密斯回忆，汤姆林森在下午七点左右离开纪念碑站外面的报摊<ref name="BrownApril9" />。《[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]》刊登的图像显示他在警车前抽烟<ref>{{cite news | url = http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2009/04/09/article-1168315-04607B4E000005DC-246_468x300.jpg | deadurl = no | title = Tomlinson photograph 1 | newspaper = Daily Mail | date = 2009-04-10 | accessdate = 2019-10-08 | archivedate = 2019-10-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191008020930/https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2009/04/09/article-1168315-04607B4E000005DC-246_468x300.jpg }}</ref>。IT工作者罗斯·哈迪（{{lang|en|Ross Hardy}}）自称在[[朗伯德街|朗伯德街]]看到汤姆林森醉醺醺的而且拒不挪窝，警车往前碰到他的腿，但他还是不动，于是四名穿戴防护装备的警察上前把他架开<ref name="Mahaffey26Aug2010p126" />。《每日邮报》刊登的第二张图像显示汤姆林森和身后两名警察<ref>{{cite web | url = http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2009/04/09/article-1168315-04607D73000005DC-487_468x286.jpg | accessdate = 2019-10-08 | deadurl = yes | title = Tomlinson photograph 2 | newspaper = Daily Mail | date = 2009-04-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191008020929/https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2009/04/09/article-1168315-04607D73000005DC-487_468x286.jpg | archivedate = 2019-10-08 }}</ref>。4月16日，《卫报》刊登三幅汤姆林森在朗伯德街的图像<ref>{{cite web | title = Tomlinson photograph 1 | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180820103234/http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2009/4/16/1239897944968/Ian-Tomlinson-at-7.08pm-o-001.jpg | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2018-08-20 | url = http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2009/4/16/1239897944968/Ian-Tomlinson-at-7.08pm-o-001.jpg | deadurl = no }}
* {{cite web | title = photograph 2 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2018-12-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181228095341/https://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2009/4/16/1239898035689/Ian-Tomlinson-at-7.10pm-o-001.jpg | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-16 | url = http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2009/4/16/1239898035689/Ian-Tomlinson-at-7.10pm-o-001.jpg }}
* {{cite web | title = photograph 3 | newspaper = The Guardian | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031035616/https://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2009/4/16/1239898122480/Ian-Tomlinson-walks-away--001.jpg | archivedate = 2020-10-31 | date = 2009-04-16 | url = http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2009/4/16/1239898122480/Ian-Tomlinson-walks-away--001.jpg }}</ref><ref name="LewisApril16">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | date = 2009-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612144628/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/16/ian-tomlinson-g20-photographs | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/16/ian-tomlinson-g20-photographs | title = New Ian Tomlinson photos show police contact before video clash | newspaper = The Guardian | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。

在朗伯德街停留半小时后，汤姆林森走向[[威廉王街|威廉王街]]，前方有两条警戒线，警察已将英格兰银行附近数以千计的示威者“包抄”于此。他在下午19点10分原路折回，打算走交易所巷，但这里同样有警戒线。五分钟后他回到朗伯德街，穿过大街并走进伯钦巷（{{lang|en|Birchin Lane}}），19点10至15分抵达[[康希尔|康希尔]]。<ref name="BrownApril9" />

几分钟后，他到达皇家交易所通道行人专用区北端，靠近[[针线街|针线街]]交界处，但又被警戒线挡住去路。他转朝皇家交易所通道向南，警察几分钟前在此与多达25名示威者发生冲突。就在这时，伦敦警察厅地区支援课防暴警察与伦敦市警局携带警犬的训犬员从针线街警戒现场赶来协助同僚。<ref name="BrownApril9" /><ref name="GammellApril18">{{cite news | author = Caroline Gammell | title = G20: The last moments of Ian Tomlinson | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5173455/G20-The-last-moments-of-Ian-Tomlinson.html | deadurl = no | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2009-04-18 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009051852/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5173455/G20-The-last-moments-of-Ian-Tomlinson.html | archivedate = 2016-10-09 }}</ref>

