汤姆林森在不到50米的街上行走，身后是大群警察<ref name="BrownApril9" />。他朝针线街前进，但又被警戒线阻挡，于是回头走向康希尔<ref name="GammellApril18" />。[[英格蘭及威爾斯皇家檢控署|皇家检控署]]的报告称他下午7点15分被警犬咬中腿部，当时训犬员叫他让路，但他没有反应<ref name="CPSstatement" />。

汤姆林森在皇家交易所通道最南端、与康希尔交汇处附近的万宝龙专卖店外遇到之前跟在身后这群警察<ref name="BrownApril9" />。他双手插在袋里，目击者称他当时表示想回家<ref name="Lewishelper"/>。

《卫报》首发的视频显示警察从身后冲向汤姆林森，用警棍打他的腿并把受害人推倒。4月8日，《第四台新聞》另发视频，显示警察手持警棍举至头高，然后一挥而下打中汤姆林森的腿<ref name="SecondvideoApril8">{{cite news | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/video/2009/apr/08/g20-police-assault-ian-tomlinson-video | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101045852/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/video/2009/apr/08/g20-police-assault-ian-tomlinson-video | title = Ian Tomlinson death: New video footage from G20 protests gives fresh angle on attack | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-08 | archivedate = 2020-11-01 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。4月21日《卫报》再发视频，显示警察冲上来时汤姆林森站在自行车架旁，双手插在兜里。视频表明他倒地后额头右侧与地面刮擦，目击者称听到头撞到地面的声音。<ref name="Guardian Cornhill video">{{cite news | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/video/2009/apr/21/g20-ian-tomlinson-new-video | title = New G20 video shows Ian Tomlinson’s head hit ground | at = 01:09 | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201103175928/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/video/2009/apr/21/g20-ian-tomlinson-new-video | archivedate = 2020-11-03 | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = John Domokos | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Lewis22April2009">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200910174039/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/22/new-ian-tomlinson-g20-video | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/22/new-ian-tomlinson-g20-video | title = G20 protest footage shows moment Ian Tomlinson's head hit the pavement | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-22 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2020-09-10 }}</ref>

=== 倒地死亡 ===
视频显示汤姆林森倒地后一度坐在地上抗议，但没有警察上前扶持<ref name="inquestJune2009">{{cite web | title = Briefing on the death of Ian Tomlinson | work = INQUEST | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171210015551/http://www.statewatch.org/news/2009/jun/uk-tomlinson-inquest-briefing-jun-09.pdf | date = 2009-06 | format = pdf | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2017-12-10 | url = https://www.statewatch.org/media/documents/news/2009/jun/uk-tomlinson-inquest-briefing-jun-09.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|11}}。示威者将他扶起，汤姆林森沿康希尔前行约60米后于下午7点22分在康希尔77号路边倒地。目击者称他看起来显得茫然，眼睛上翻，皮肤灰白，还闻到他身上的酒味。<ref name="Mahaffey26Aug2010p126" /><ref name="BrownApril9" />《[[ITV新闻|ITV新闻]]》摄影师想叫医生，但和医学院学生一样被警察赶开<ref name="BrownApril9" /><ref>{{cite news | author = Martha Kearney | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NPqLf26arFU | title = G20 Protest - Ian Tomlinson Death - Witness Statement Lucy Apps on | work = [[BBC廣播四台|BBC Radio 4 News]] | date = 2009-04-09 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archive-date = 2021-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117114204/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NPqLf26arFU | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="RaynerSwaineApril9">{{cite news | author1 = Gordon Rayner | author2 = Jon Swaine | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2009-04-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160414111620/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5126270/G20-death-Ian-Tomlinsons-final-moments.html | title = G20 death: Ian Tomlinson's final moments | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/5126270/G20-death-Ian-Tomlinsons-final-moments.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-14 }}</ref>。警方医务人员上前检查，受害者抵达医院后被宣告死亡<ref name="LewisLaville">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = Sandra Laville | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031030100/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/apr/06/g20-ian-tomlinson-police-assault | url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/apr/06/g20-ian-tomlinson-police-assault | title = G20: Police question witness to alleged assault on man who died during protests | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-06 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2020-10-31 }}</ref>。

== 西蒙·哈伍德 ==
=== 背景 ===
[[不合法被殺|行凶杀人]]的西蒙·哈伍德（{{lang|en|Simon Harwood}}）是[[兰贝斯|兰贝斯]]拉克霍尔巷（{{lang|en|Larkhall Lane}}）警局地区支援课警员<ref>{{cite news | title = Ian Tomlinson death: Simon Harwood cleared of manslaughter | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/19/simon-harwood-not-guilty-ian-tomlinson | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201103153915/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/19/simon-harwood-not-guilty-ian-tomlinson | date = 2012-07-19 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | newspaper = The Guardian | archivedate = 2020-11-03 | author1 = Peter Walker | author2 = Paul Lewis }}</ref><ref name="Inquest verdict">{{cite news | title = Ian Tomlinson inquest verdict | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/blog/2011/may/03/ian-tomlinson-inquest-verdict-live-blog | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-05-03 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030165220/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/blog/2011/may/03/ian-tomlinson-inquest-verdict-live-blog | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="LewisLaville2April9">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = Sandra Laville | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/09/g20-ian-tomlinson-police-video | title = G20 death: Met police officer breaks cover | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030214615/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/09/g20-ian-tomlinson-police-video | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 }}</ref>，过去12年间十次受投诉<ref name="Peachey19July2012">{{cite news | author = Paul Peachey | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191218151018/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/pc-simon-harwood-10-complaints-in-12-years-for-the-red-mist-officer-7959576.html | newspaper = The Independent | date = 2012-07-19 | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/pc-simon-harwood-10-complaints-12-years-red-mist-officer-7959576.html | title = Pc Simon Harwood – 10 complaints in 12 years for the 'red mist' officer | archivedate = 2019-12-18 }}</ref>，其中九次不成立或无法证实，另一次涉及非法访问[[国家警察计算机网络|国家警察计算机网络]]<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/20/police-simon-harwood-disciplinary-records?intcmp=239 | author = Paul Lewis | title = Tomlinson case: Met police tried to hide PC Harwood's disciplinary record | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2012-07-19 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2020-11-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201104230440/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/20/police-simon-harwood-disciplinary-records?intcmp=239 }}</ref>。不成立或未证实投诉包括1998年左右的路怒事件，他在病假期间逮捕司机，对方指控哈伍德动用不必要的武力。2001年9月14日，他在纪律委员会即将聆讯前以身体健康为由退役。<ref name="Peachey19July2012" /><ref name="Laville1">{{cite news | author = Sandra Laville | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160927190157/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/jul/05/query-g20-assault-case-officer | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/jul/05/query-g20-assault-case-officer | title = Disciplinary query over G20 assault case officer | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-07-05 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2016-09-27 }}</ref>三天后（9月17日），他又作为平民计算机工作者加入伦敦警察厅<ref name="Peachey19July2012" />。

2003年5月，哈伍德成为萨里郡警局警员，该警队称他对过去的问题坦然承认。2004年1月，有消息称哈伍德在突击民宅时袭击某男子。<ref name="Peachey19July2012" />2004年11月，哈伍德获许调回伦敦警察厅<ref name="Gammell22July">{{cite news | author1 = Caroline Gammell | author2 = Andrew Hough | author3 = Gordon Rayner | title = G20 riots: Policeman who stuck Ian Tomlinson faced two previous aggression inquiries | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100725071303/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/financetopics/g20-summit/7905549/G20-riots-Policeman-who-stuck-Ian-Tomlinson-faced-two-previous-aggression-inquiries.html | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2010-07-23 | archivedate = 2010-07-25 | accessdate = 2010-07-25 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/financetopics/g20-summit/7905549/G20-riots-Policeman-who-stuck-Ian-Tomlinson-faced-two-previous-aggression-inquiries.html }}</ref>。遇上汤姆林森之前，哈伍德还遇到三次投诉<ref name="Peachey19July2012" />。

=== 事发当日 ===
事发当天，哈伍德涉及多起警民对抗。他从清晨五点就开始上班，负责开车，这天大部分时间都在车上。晚上停在康希尔时，他看到有人在另一辆警车侧面写上“警察都是混蛋”（{{lang|en|all cops are bastards}}）字样后下车想要将其逮捕。嫌犯的头撞到车门，抗议人群反应强烈，哈伍德觉得此时返-{回}-车上太不安全。他一度向调查人员自称被打到头、摔倒、丢失警棍，面对暴民攻击担心会被打死，但后来承认根本没这些事。<ref name="Lewis3May"/><ref name="LewisSharrock4May">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = David Sharrock | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160927190415/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/apr/04/ian-tomlinson-inquest-simon-harwood?intcmp=239 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2016-09-27 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/apr/04/ian-tomlinson-inquest-simon-harwood?intcmp=239 | title = Ian Tomlinson inquest hears police officer feared for his life | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-05-04 }}</ref>

尝试逮捕涂鸦男后不久，哈伍德向示威者挥动外套，又把英国广播公司摄影师拖倒在地，还以手掌打人，并在下午7点19分把据称威胁警方驯犬员的男子推倒在地。几秒钟后，哈伍德看到站在自行车架旁、双手插进口袋的汤姆林森，其他警察正叫他走开。哈伍德向调查人员表示，他在那一刻以为有必要行动，所以上前用警棍打中受害人大腿并将其推倒。他承认不该推人，看到汤姆林森倒地时吓了一跳。<ref name="Lewis3May" />哈伍德没有把事件经过记入笔记，一度向调查人员自称已经忘记当时情况<ref name="Lewis3May">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/03/ian-tomlinson-verdict-jury-decision?INTCMP=SRCH | title = Ian Tomlinson verdict: Jury decision is severe indictment for police officer | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030122907/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/03/ian-tomlinson-verdict-jury-decision?INTCMP=SRCH | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | date = 2011-05-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 身份指认 ===
事发三个多月后，报纸才在2010年7月公布肇事者是哈伍德<ref name="DoddJuly22">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200710141000/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/ian-tomlinson-police-not-charged | author1 = Vikram Dodd | author2 = Paul Lewis | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2020-07-10 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/ian-tomlinson-police-not-charged | title = Ian Tomlinson death: police officer will not face criminal charges | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2010-07-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。事发当天他应该是把肩章编号撕掉，还用巴拉克拉瓦头套遮住大部分头脸<ref name="LewisLaville2April9" />。《每日邮报》公布的图像显示他的肩部没有编号<ref name="auto">{{cite web | date = 2009-04-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191008020929/https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2009/04/09/article-1168315-0460FDED000005DC-902_468x341.jpg | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archivedate = 2019-10-08 | deadurl = no | url = https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2009/04/09/article-1168315-0460FDED000005DC-902_468x341.jpg | title = Photograph | newspaper = Daily Mail }}</ref>。2009年4月22日，《[[第四台新闻|第四台新闻]]》的西蒙·以色列（{{lang|en|Simon Israel}}）在报导中详细描述涉案警员；独立监察警方处理投诉委员会宣称这些内容可能影响调查，但未能对第四台的节目取得禁令<ref name="IsraelApril22">{{cite news | author = Simon Israel | title = Exclusive: new G20 video evidence | url = https://www.channel4.com/news/exclusive-new-g20-video-evidence | accessdate = 2020-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305152021/http://www.channel4.com/news/exclusive-new-g20-video-evidence | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | work = Channel 4 News | date = 2009-04-22 }}</ref>。15个月后，皇家检控署2010年7月宣布不起诉时仍称他为“警员甲”<ref name="CPSstatement" />，报社正是这天决定点名<ref name="DoddJuly22" />。

哈伍德自称4月8日看到《卫报》公布的视频时才知汤姆林森已死。据称他在家中倒地，被救护车送到医院。<ref>{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191231082256/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/17/ian-tomlinson-g20-protest-coroner | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/17/ian-tomlinson-g20-protest-coroner | title = Tomlinson officer questioned on suspicion of manslaughter | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2019-12-31 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = David Randall | title = Ian Tomlinson: The man who was trying to get home | newspaper = The Independent on Sunday | date = 2009-04-12 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180221101839/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/ian-tomlinson-the-man-who-was-trying-to-get-home-1667554.html | archivedate = 2018-02-21 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/ian-tomlinson-the-man-who-was-trying-to-get-home-1667554.html }}</ref>这天他和三名同事向独立监察警方处理投诉委员会自承身份<ref name="DoddLewisApril9">{{cite news | author1 = Vikram Dodd | author2 = Paul Lewis | title = G20 death: Police officer suspended | newspaper = The Guardian | deadurl = no | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/09/g20-death-police-officer-suspended | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101220136/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/09/g20-death-police-officer-suspended | date = 2009-04-09 | archivedate = 2020-11-01 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 }}</ref>。

