=== 警方首次声明 ===
4月1日晚23点36分，伦敦警察厅在汤姆林森死亡四小时后首次发布独立监察警方处理投诉委员会伦敦地区总监批准的声明，声称警察得知有人倒地后顶着“许多投掷物品”马上施救，但后来的媒体报导认为上述说法不尽不实{{refn|group="注"|2009年4月1日23:36，伦敦警察厅：{{Paragraph break}}“伯钦巷与康希尔交汇处警戒线的警察接到市民报告，某男子在街角附近倒地不起，该警员派两名警方医务人员前去查看，他们经过警戒线进入圣迈克尔斯巷（{{lang|en|St Michaels Alley}}）后看到男子已停止呼吸，在19点30分左右呼叫伦敦救护车支援。警方初步检查并清理他的呼吸道，然后把他转移到皇家交易所外警戒线后的开阔地，再对他[[心肺复苏|心肺复苏]]。警方当时受到许多投掷物品（估计是瓶子）袭击，所以决定将他转移。伦敦救护车把男子送到医院，但医院宣告他已经死亡。”<ref>{{cite news | title = G20 fatality: How police view of Ian Tomlinson death changed | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031001439/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/08/ian-tomlinson-g20-death-official-police-account | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-08 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/08/ian-tomlinson-g20-death-official-police-account | archivedate = 2020-10-31 }}</ref><ref name="inquestJune2009" />{{rp|4}}}}。

[[尼克·戴维斯|尼克·戴维斯]]（{{lang|en|Nick Davies}}）在《卫报》发文，称伦敦警察厅新闻发布办事处原本的新闻稿遭否决，经过激烈争论后发布上述声明。文中还称，伦敦警察厅和独立监察警方处理投诉委员会宣称内容如实反映他们当时所知的情况，而且没有听说受害人曾与警方肢体接触。载维斯质疑，如果真的不知道肢体接触，独立监察警方处理投诉委员会又怎么会介入。他还称，伦敦警察厅内部高管私下透露，[[南伦敦|南伦敦]]科博尔特街（{{lang|en|Cobalt Street}}）警察控制局人员当时发现汤姆林森挨打，还有行动现场[[總督察|總督察]]上报。伦敦警察厅的声明宣称已经向参与格伦科行动的所有总督察核实，但没有人上报此事。<ref name="DaviesApril27">{{cite news | author = Nick Davies | url = https://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/apr/27/ipcc-police-g20-death-media | title = Can the police and the media trust each other? | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191120053423/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/apr/27/ipcc-police-g20-death-media | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2019-11-20 }}</ref>{{refn|group="注"|独立监察警方处理投诉委员会当时的指导方针是：如果出现“警察直接或间接导致人员重伤或死亡，或有理由相信警方接触导致或部分导致人员重伤或死亡”，事件应交独立监察警方处理投诉委员会调查<ref name="DaviesApril27" />。}}

=== 第一目击者陈述 ===
[[File:Evening_Standard_headline_about_Ian_Tomlinson,_April_2_2009.JPG|thumb]]

4月2日，伦敦警察厅将调查任务移交伦敦市警察局，新的负责警官是安东尼·克兰普顿（{{lang|en|Anthony Crampton}}）[[警司|警司]]<ref name="LewisMay92011">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/09/ian-tomlinson-evidence-held-back | title = Ian Tomlinson evidence was held back from IPCC | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-05-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201104145812/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/09/ian-tomlinson-evidence-held-back | archivedate = 2020-11-04 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。警方通报后，《标准晚报》当天报称警方顶着“砖头、瓶子和木板的狂轰滥炸”拼命救护汤姆林森，冒着飞来的投掷物品将他转移到安全地点后人工呼吸施救<ref>{{cite news | author1 = Justin Davenport | author2 = Danny Brierley | newspaper = Evening Standard | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110719071853/http://www.chickyog.net/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/esp67-02042009.pdf | url = https://www.questia.com/newspaper/1G1-196972490/police-pelted-with-bricks-as-they-help-dying-man | title = Police pelted with bricks as they help dying man | date = 2009-04-02 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | via = Questia | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2011-07-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author1 = Justin Davenport | author2 = Danny Brierley | url = https://www.standard.co.uk/news/ring-of-steel-keeps-demos-away-from-world-leaders-6897646.html | title = Ring of steel keeps demos away from world leaders | newspaper = Evening Standard | date = 2009-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821183141/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/ring-of-steel-keeps-demos-away-from-world-leaders-6897646.html | archivedate = 2016-08-21 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

目击者称警方说法不实，是抗议者上前急救并致电求医<ref name="Indymediawitnesses">{{cite news | deadurl = yes | url = https://london.indymedia.org.uk/videos/1023 | title = Witness Statement About G20 Death | accessdate = 2014-11-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129040748/https://london.indymedia.org.uk/videos/1023 | archivedate = 2014-11-29 | newspaper = Indymedia London | date = 2009-04-02 }}</ref>。还有人称，的确有人在不知道汤姆林森倒地的情况下扔出一两个塑料瓶，但其他示威者马上叫他们住手<ref name="LewisWilliamsJones">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = Rachel Williams | author3 = Sam Jones | url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/apr/02/g20-summit-protester-death | title = Police name man who died at G20 protest | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-02 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200519142349/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/apr/02/g20-summit-protester-death | archivedate = 2020-05-19 }}</ref>。《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》分析电视录像和照片后认为，人群扔出的只有一个瓶子，而且很可能是塑料瓶<ref name="BrownApril9" />。4月9日，《卫报》发布目击者纳贝拉·扎希尔（{{lang|en|Nabeela Zahir}}）拍摄的视频，显示击威者大喊“有人受伤了，快他妈退开！”另有人喊：“有人受伤了，别扔东西！”<ref name="NabeelaZahirvideo">{{cite news | title = New G20 video compounds doubts over police account of Ian Tomlinson's death | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/09/g20-video-ian-tomlinson-death | author1 = Paul Lewis | author2 = Peter Walker | date = 2009-04-09 | newspaper = The Guardian | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200627104528/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/09/g20-video-ian-tomlinson-death | archivedate = 2020-06-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

