三名警员均未认出哈伍德，都根据报纸文章推测他是伦敦市警局人员，《卫报》四天后公布视频。4月3日下午16点15分，琼斯督查将信息转告伦敦警察厅当时负责案件调查的埃迪·霍尔（{{lang|en|Eddie Hall}}）督查。霍尔自称在弗雷迪·帕特尔（{{lang|en|Freddy Patel}}）开始首轮验尸前把信息转达伦敦市警局，据《卫报》所述，验尸是在下午17点开始。<ref name="LewisMay92011" />

== 死因研讯 ==
2009年4月9日，伦敦市警局验尸官保罗·马修斯（{{lang|en|Paul Matthews}}）启动[[死因研讯|死因研讯]]，之后共经过三轮验尸：4月3日穆罕默德·赛义德·苏勒马·“弗雷迪”·帕特尔（{{lang|en|Mohmed Saeed Sulema "Freddy" Patel}}）验尸并向保罗·马修斯汇报；4月9日纳撒尼尔·卡里（{{lang|en|Nathaniel Cary}}）验尸并向独立监察警方处理投诉委员会和死者家属汇报；4月22日肯尼斯·索罗克（{{lang|en|Kenneth Shorrock}}）和本·斯威夫特（{{lang|en|Ben Swift}}）一起验尸，分别向伦敦警察厅和西蒙·哈伍德汇报。马修斯因未通知独立监察警方处理投诉委员会调查员参与首轮验尸，也未告知受害者亲属有法定权力亲自或派代表检视验尸过程受到批评。汤姆林斯的家人称，马修斯根本没告诉他们是在哪里验尸。<ref name="Dodd23July">{{cite news | author = Vikram Dodd | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/23/ian-tomlinson-death-inquest-coroner | title = Ian Tomlinson coroner is urged to stand aside | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2010-07-23 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201102202535/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/23/ian-tomlinson-death-inquest-coroner | archivedate = 2020-11-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

=== 首轮验尸 ===
伦敦市警局钱德勒（{{lang|en|Chandler}}）警司声称，他是在首轮验尸结束后才得知三名警察看到其他警察击打并推倒受害人，帕特尔和独立监察警方处理投诉委员会显然对三名警察的证词一无所知。帕特尔称，他知道的只是死者“死因可疑”，而且警方要求他“排除任何维持公共秩序可能导致的击打或冲撞”。<ref name="LewisMay92011" /><ref>{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101034408/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/09/tomlinson-police-witness-baton-attack | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/09/tomlinson-police-witness-baton-attack | title = Ian Tomlinson: key evidence that police withheld from coroner, IPCC and family | date = 2011-05-09 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-11-01 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 }}</ref><ref name="inquestJune2009" />{{rp|4–5}}

帕特尔的结论是汤姆林森死于[[冠狀動脈疾病|冠狀動脈疾病]]，报告上称“腹腔积液约三升并有小血块”，据医学专业人士解讯，这表明受害人腹部积血三升，相当于血液总量六成之多，皇家检控署认为这显然很可能就是死因。2010年4月5日，帕特尔在事发一年后向皇家检控署递交报告，称他原本验尸报告上那句话的意思是“带血的腹腔积液有三升”，而且他没有取样检验。皇家检控署后来决定不起诉哈伍德，帕特尔的报告及所谓“腹腔积液”内容不明影响举足轻重。<ref name="CPSstatement" /><ref name="Syal22July2010">{{cite news | author1 = Rajeev Syal | author2 = Amelia Hill | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/case-against-police-officer-tomlinson-death | title = How the case against a police officer over Tomlinson death fell apart | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200712052734/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/case-against-police-officer-tomlinson-death | date = 2010-07-22 | accessdate = 2020-07-12 | archivedate = 2020-07-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Walker26June2012">{{cite news | author = Peter Walker | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200924035310/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jun/26/ian-tomlinson-pathologist-forensic-evidence | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jun/26/ian-tomlinson-pathologist-forensic-evidence | date = 2012-06-26 | title = Ian Tomlinson pathologist threw away forensic evidence, court told | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-09-24 }}</ref>4月4日，伦敦市警局发布声明：“验尸表明他是在下班回家的路上突发心脏病自然死亡”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/london/7982855.stm | title = G20 death man 'had heart attack' | work = BBC News | date = 2009-04-04 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201104075321/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/london/7982855.stm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-11-04 }}</ref>。

独立监察警方处理投诉委员会向记者宣称，验尸没有在死者头部和两肩发现瘀伤或擦伤<ref name="FrescoONeillApril10">{{cite news | author1 = Adam Fresco | author2 = Sean O'Neill | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | title = Officer suspended in investigation into G20 death of Ian Tomlinson | newspaper = The Times | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/officer-suspended-in-investigation-into-g20-death-of-ian-tomlinson-kv5bdtk8snn | date = 2009-04-10 | archive-date = 2021-02-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210206021549/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/officer-suspended-in-investigation-into-g20-death-of-ian-tomlinson-kv5bdtk8snn | dead-url = no }}</ref>。首轮验尸后，汤姆林森的家人询问伦敦市警局尸体上是否有伤痕，回答是否；据《卫报》报导，负责调查的安东尼·克兰普顿警司在笔记中写道，他有意向家属隐瞒死者腿上的瘀伤和刺痕，目的是不想引起“不必要的压力和紧张”<ref name="Judd">{{cite news | author = Terry Judd | newspaper = The Independent | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171023174202/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/new-evidence-of-police-attacks-on-g20-victim-1666116.html | title = New evidence of police attacks on G20 victim | date = 2009-04-09 | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/new-evidence-of-police-attacks-on-g20-victim-1666116.html | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2017-10-23 }}</ref>。4月5日，《[[观察家报|观察家报]]》发布第一张受害人躺在防暴警察身边地面的照片<ref name="TownsendApril52009">{{cite news | author1 = Mark Townsend | author2 = Paul Lewis | url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/apr/05/g20-protest-ian-tomlinson | title = Police 'assaulted' bystander who died during G20 protests | newspaper = The Observer | date = 2009-04-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200928144938/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/apr/05/g20-protest-ian-tomlinson | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-09-28 }}</ref>。接下来弗雷迪·帕特尔受命再度检视尸体，记下死者头部的瘀伤，据称先前验尸时他没有发现这里的伤势<ref name="LewisMay92011" />。4月24日，[[天空新闻台|天空新闻台]]取得汤姆林森倒地后的照片，能看到他右侧额头的瘀伤<ref name="Skypic24April2009">{{cite news | url = http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/G20-Protest-Picture-Shows-Ian-Tomlinson-Had-Head-Injury-After-Being-Pushed-To-Ground-By-Police/Article/200904415268375?lpos=UK_News_Carousel_Region_0&lid=ARTICLE_15268375_G20_Protest_Picture_Shows_Ian_Tomlinson_Had_Head_Injury_After_Being_Pushed_To_Ground_By_Police | author = Martin Brunt | accessdate = 2009-04-27 | archivedate = 2009-04-27 | date = 2009-04-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090427071243/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/G20-Protest-Picture-Shows-Ian-Tomlinson-Had-Head-Injury-After-Being-Pushed-To-Ground-By-Police/Article/200904415268375?lpos=UK_News_Carousel_Region_0&lid=ARTICLE_15268375_G20_Protest_Picture_Shows_Ian_Tomlinson_Had_Head_Injury_After_Being_Pushed_To_Ground_By_Police | title = Pic Shows G20 Protest Victim's Head Injury | work = [[天空新闻台|Sky News]] | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = David Pallister | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031073755/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/24/ian-tomlinson-g20-protest-death | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/24/ian-tomlinson-g20-protest-death | title = New Ian Tomlinson photo appears to show head injury before G20 death | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-24 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-10-31 }}</ref>。

=== 第二和第三轮验尸 ===
4月8日，独立监察警方处理投诉委员会从伦敦市警局接手调查。根据委员会和死者家属共同要求，以参与多起高关注度案件调查闻名的纳撒尼尔·卡里开展第二轮验尸<ref name="LewisDoddApril10/2">{{cite news | author1 = Paul Lewis Lewis | author2 = Vikram Dodd | date = 2009-04-10 | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191007005410/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/10/g20-assault-investigation | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/10/g20-assault-investigation | title = Ian Tomlinson death: G20 riot officer in footage has not been interviewed | archivedate = 2019-10-07 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。卡里认为汤姆林森死于钝器外伤引发的腹内出血，死者所患肝硬化也有影响<ref name="DoddCary22July">{{cite news | author = Vikram Dodd | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/second-expert-pc-actions-g20-death | title = Second expert has 'no doubt' PC's actions contributed to G20 death | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171015203423/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/second-expert-pc-actions-g20-death | date = 2010-07-22 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2017-10-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他的结论是：死者摔倒时手肘正撞在肝部并引发内出血，导致他在几分钟后死亡<ref name="Rayner22July">{{cite news | author1 = Gordon Rayner | author2 = Caroline Gammell | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2010-07-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171018075411/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/7904244/G20-riots-policeman-escapes-charges-over-Ian-Tomlinsons-death.html | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2017-10-18 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/7904244/G20-riots-policeman-escapes-charges-over-Ian-Tomlinsons-death.html | title = G20 riots: policeman escapes charges over Ian Tomlinson's death | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

前两次验尸结果相互冲突，4月22日肯尼斯·索罗克和本·斯威夫特一起验尸，分别向伦敦警察厅和西蒙·哈伍德汇报。索罗克和斯威夫特都认可第二次验尸的结果。埃迪·霍尔在最后一次验尸前告诉两位验尸的病理学家，死者4月1日下午在警车前摔倒，但没有任何证据支持他的说法。2011年5月，独立监察警方处理投诉委员会裁定霍尔的说法说于鲁莽，但无意误导。<ref name="LewisIPCCMay92011">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/09/ian-tomlinson-death | title = IPCC rules Met officer 'reckless' in conduct | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-05-09 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-11-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201102045449/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/09/ian-tomlinson-death | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | title = Ian Tomlinson - Metropolitan Police Service | date = 2009-04 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/investigations/ian-tomlinson-metropolitan-police-service | work = IPCC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170703113900/http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/investigations/ian-tomlinson-metropolitan-police-service | accessdate = 2017-07-03 | archivedate = 2017-07-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | work = IPCC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130724103604/http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/en/Documents/pathologists_090511.pdf | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2013-07-24 | url = http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/en/Documents/pathologists_090511.pdf | title = Complaint that misinformation was supplied | date = 2010-04-20 | archivedate = 2013-07-24 | format = PDF }}</ref>

=== 弗雷迪·帕特尔 ===
汤姆林森去世时，帕特尔是内政部认可登记的[[法医病理学|法医病理学家]]。他于1974年取得[[赞比亚大学|赞比亚大学]]博士学位，1988年开始在英国注册执业<ref name="Bowcott12July">{{cite news | author = Owen Bowcott | deadurl = no | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/12/ian-tomlinson-pathologist-accused-incompetence-autopsies | title = Ian Tomlinson pathologist accused of incompetence over autopsies | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030024108/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/12/ian-tomlinson-pathologist-accused-incompetence-autopsies | date = 2010-07-12 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-10-30 }}</ref>。伦敦警察厅曾于2005年咨询内政部，质疑帕特尔的工作能力。汤姆林森去世时，帕特尔没有对可疑死因验尸的警方委聘合同<ref name="Lewis22July">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030040722/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/ian-tomlinson-story-justice-denied | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/22/ian-tomlinson-story-justice-denied | title = Ian Tomlinson: a story of justice denied | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2010-07-22 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-07 }}</ref>。

1999年，[[罗杰·西尔维斯特之死|罗杰·西尔维斯特]]（{{lang|en|Roger Sylvester}}）在警方拘押期间死亡，帕特尔因擅自公布死者医疗细节受[[醫學總會_(英國)|医学总会]]训诫<ref name="Bowcott12July" />。2002年，[[安东尼·哈迪|安东尼·哈迪]]（{{lang|en|Anthony Hardy}}）上锁的公寓房间内发现女尸，据称死者莎莉·怀特（{{lang|en|Sally White}}）身上不着寸缕且有瘀伤，头部也有伤口，大腿有咬伤痕迹，但因帕特尔称受害人死于心脏病，没有暴力侵犯迹象，警方取消刑事调查。哈迪酗酒且有精神病，之后又谋杀两名女子，将肢解的尸体放在垃圾袋。<ref>{{cite news | author = Richard Osley | url = http://www.camdennewjournal.co.uk/archive/n271103_2.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305174545/http://camdennewjournal.co.uk/archive/n271103_2.htm | title = Inquest dismissed ‘signs of violence’ | newspaper = Camden New Journal | date = 2003-11-27 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2016-03-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref><ref name="Lewis11April2009">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/11/g20-pathologist-ian-tomlinson | title = Pathologist in Ian Tomlinson G20 death case was reprimanded over conduct | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-04-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200902200539/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/apr/11/g20-pathologist-ian-tomlinson | archivedate = 2020-09-02 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>警方一度调查帕特尔的验尸情况，但之后放弃<ref name="GammellPatel">{{cite news | author = Caroline Gammell | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190705181917/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/7904804/G20-riots-profile-of-Dr-Freddy-Patel.html | deadurl = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/g20-summit/7904804/G20-riots-profile-of-Dr-Freddy-Patel.html | title = G20 riots: profile of Dr Freddy Patel | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2010-07-23 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2019-07-05 }}</ref>。面对批评，帕特尔声称医学总会的训诫早已是陈年旧事，他对莎莉·怀特死因的判断从未受质疑<ref name="Lewis11April2009" />。

2009年7月，政府暂停帕特尔的注册病理学家资格，等待医学总会质询<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/financetopics/g20-summit/5749486/Officer-under-investigation-over-Ian-Tomlinsons-death-should-not-have-been-working-for-Met.html | author = Ian Johnston | accessdate = 2010-07-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100703063946/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/financetopics/g20-summit/5749486/Officer-under-investigation-over-Ian-Tomlinsons-death-should-not-have-been-working-for-Met.html | title = Officer under investigation over Ian Tomlinson's death 'should not have been working for Met' | newspaper = The Sunday Telegraph | date = 2009-07-05 | archivedate = 2010-07-03 }}</ref>。质询包括针对另外四起案件验尸结果的26项指控，其中一项是五岁女童在家中摔死后帕特尔既未发现尸体上的虐待痕迹，也未向医院了解死者伤势。当局后来掘出尸体再次验尸，法庭最后裁定孩子的母亲罪名成立。<ref name="GammellPatel" />2010年8月听证会结束，决定将“职业表现不足”的帕特尔停职三个月<ref name="Lewis6Sept">{{cite news | author = Paul Lewis | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171015203455/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/sep/06/ian-tomlinson-coroner-inquest | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/sep/06/ian-tomlinson-coroner-inquest | title = Ian Tomlinson coroner asks for judge to preside over inquest | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2010-09-06 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2017-10-15 }}</ref>。2011年5月，医学总会又开始调查他对汤普林森验尸的表现<ref>{{cite news | author1 = Owen Bowcott | author2 = Paul Lewis | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030042700/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/05/freddy-patel-investigated-ian-tomlinson-autopsy | title = Pathologist Freddy Patel investigated over Ian Tomlinson postmortem | deadurl = no | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/05/freddy-patel-investigated-ian-tomlinson-autopsy | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-10-30 | date = 2011-05-05 }}</ref><ref name="Walker26June2012" />。2012年8月，医疗总会撤销他的执业资格<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-19355106 | title = Ian Tomlinson pathologist Dr Freddy Patel struck off | work = BBC News | date = 2012-08-23 | archivedate = 2020-11-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101042347/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-19355106 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

