2011年5月24日，凱爾·斯塔摩宣布已向哈伍德发出过失杀人罪传票。他还称，考虑到死因研讯发现新医学证据，而且多种医学证据（包括帕特尔提供的证据）都已经过核查，皇家检控署业已推翻之前不起诉的决定。<ref name="Starmerreview" />案件于2012年6月18日开审，哈伍德辩称罪名不成立，法庭于7月19日裁定无罪开释<ref name="WalkerLewis19July2012" />。

大量汤普林森和哈伍德的视频片段呈庭，显示哈伍德试图逮捕在警车涂鸦的人，然后与其他警察在皇家交易所通道清场。哈伍德把朝他吹奏[[呜呜祖拉|呜呜祖拉]]的男子推开，然后又将拍摄他人被捕画面的英国广播公司摄影师推开。视频还显示他把路上第三名男子推开，此时皇家交易所通道基本上已经没人，不久后他就和其他警察走到汤姆林森附近。<ref name="Walker19June2012">{{cite news | author = Peter Walker | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105052759/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jun/19/ian-tomlinson-jury-video | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jun/19/ian-tomlinson-jury-video | title = Ian Tomlinson jury shown video of moments before his death | date = 2012-06-19 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-11-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Victoria Ward | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2012-06-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160920094944/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/9341840/G20-protests-Tomlinson-family-weep-at-final-footage.html | title = G20 protests: Tomlinson family weep at final footage | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/9341840/G20-protests-Tomlinson-family-weep-at-final-footage.html | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2016-09-20 }}</ref>

代表控方的马克·丹尼斯（{{lang|en|Mark Dennis}}）[[御用大律师|御用大律师]]主张，哈伍德无理且毫无必要地向汤姆林森对武并导致后者死亡。《卫报》公布的视频证明死者是在挨打后倒地死亡，“时间联系明确”，受害人对警方毫无威胁，使用武力是“无端侵略行径”。<ref name="Ward">{{cite news | author = Victoria Ward | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201103153746/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/9339247/Officer-who-struck-out-at-Ian-Tomlinson-had-lost-control.html | title = Officer who struck out at Ian Tomlinson had 'lost control' | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/9339247/Officer-who-struck-out-at-Ian-Tomlinson-had-lost-control.html | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2012-06-18 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-11-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>辩方的帕特里克·吉布斯（{{lang|en|Patrick Gibbs}}）御用大律师主张，法庭应当考虑死者的身体情况。汤姆林森因酗酒导致肝病和脑部疾病，他双腿麻木而且难以保持平衡，2007至2009年间至少接受20次治疗，其中大部分是在醉酒跌倒后送到急诊室。据《泰晤士报》报导，受害人死亡当天喝下整瓶红酒和小瓶伏特加，还有多罐9%的超高强度啤酒。<ref>{{cite news | title = Tomlinson's sudden death 'did not obey any of the medical rules' | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/tomlisons-sudden-death-did-not-obey-any-of-the-medical-rules-666ld5n8zzg | date = 2012-07-20 | newspaper = The Times | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archive-date = 2021-02-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210206022155/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/tomlisons-sudden-death-did-not-obey-any-of-the-medical-rules-666ld5n8zzg | dead-url = no }}</ref>

哈伍德作证时称，警方要求汤姆林森走开，但他置之不理。他承认用力推向死者，但没想到汤姆林森会倒地。<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/02/ian-tomlinson-police-officer-court | title = Ian Tomlinson seemed deliberately obstructive, police officer tells court | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031103236/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/jul/02/ian-tomlinson-police-officer-court | date = 2012-07-02 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-10-31 | author = Peter Walker | dead-url = no }}</ref>哈伍德承认认知有误，没想到受害人身体状况如此严重。最终陪审团经过四天商议裁定罪名不成立。<ref name="WalkerLewis19July2012" />

=== 开除、民事诉讼 ===
2012年9月，伦敦警察厅在纪律听证会认定哈伍德对汤姆林森的行为严重不当后将他开除<ref>{{cite news | author = Peter Walker | url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/17/ian-tomlinson-death-simon-harwood-misconduct | title = Ian Tomlinson case: PC Simon Harwood guilty of gross misconduct | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201104144343/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/17/ian-tomlinson-death-simon-harwood-misconduct | date = 2012-09-17 | accessdate = 2020-11-07 | archivedate = 2020-11-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。汤姆林森的家人针对伦敦警察厅发起民事诉讼，该机构于2013年8月支付未公开数额的赔偿。副助理署长马克辛·德布伦纳（{{lang|en|Maxine de Brunner}}）向死者家属正式道歉，承认“西蒙·哈伍德非法使用过度武力导致汤姆林森先生死亡，令他的家人陷入悲痛”。<ref name="auto1" />

